        "mainbody": "'''Dier Ashlin''' was a male [[human]] [[Zhentilar]] soldier during the [[Time of Troubles]] in [[1358 DR]].{{cite book/Tantras|84}}\n\nHe was guarding the Temple of [[Bane]] in [[Zhentil Keep]] when the god Bane himself, in the corpse of [[Fzoul Chembryl]], arrived in the city after the disastrous [[Battle of Shadowdale]]. Ashlin, believing he was speaking to Fzoul, explained the change in the city's government after the defeat."
